{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make hair colour a protected characteristic",
        "additional_details": "As my sons get older they are learning that our society doesn\u2019t like \u201cgingers.\u201d It has become acceptable to make fun of someone who has different coloured hair. People with ginger hair should have the same protections as others who suffer abuse because of how they look or how they were born.",
        "background": "Imagine growing up constantly being picked on because of the colour of your hair. \r\nImagine being bullied and tormented because of the colour of your hair. \r\nImagine your child in tears. \r\nNot fair is it. \r\nRed heads should be protected from abuse by law.",
